Class CellList.CellNode

Object
CellNode
Enclosing class:
CellList
private class CellList.CellNode
extends Object
private inner Node class - Privacy leak note: If this private inner class was public, there would be a privacy leak. The reason being that the user could then access the nodes of a given CellList directly, from outside of the outer class. In order to avoid privacy leaks, it is best to create the Node class as a private inner class of the linked list class, and setting attributes to private.
